<a href="http://cte.uic.edu/" target="_blank">cte.uic.edu</a><br/>
Contact: (312) 355-0714<br/>
1333 S. Halsted St., Suite 205, MC 134<br/>
Hours: 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m. Monday-Friday</p>
